Getting angry makes a print, which repeats the same cycle. Anger is a weapon used in self-defense against fear. So we are not opening up by being angry. <span class=date>9/16/79</span>
<br>Q: When the mind gives a lot of trouble, you said imprison the mind. How?
<br>A: Imprison the mind means making limits on desires. <span class=date>9/20/79</span>
